ED_Title: Notification by the Secretary-General under Article 12, paragraph 2, of the Charter of the United Nations
ED_DecisionText: At its 95th plenary meeting, on 28 August 2017, the General Assembly took note of the note by the Secretary-General (A/71/300).
ED_Disclaimer: The final version of this decision will be contained in document A/71/49 (Vol. III) after editorial review.
